  <h2 id="what-is-fuel-oil">What is Fuel Oil (HFO)?</h2>

  <img
    src="/images/fuel-oil-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-Explosion-Proof-Centrifuge-600.webp"
    alt="Alfa Laval Explosion Proof Centrifuge"
    width="480"
    height="600"
